title: Projects | SIT Virtual Open House 2025/2026
text_lines: Read more about all the exciting projects that our students have been working on. Just click on the links to find out more!
This video highlights warehouse process optimisation using data analysis, programming, and engineering concepts, it enhanced process efficiency, operational sustainability, and cost savings.
This video highlights the Innovation Intern experience at CEVA Logistics, leveraging IoT, simulation modelling, and 3D printing to automate and optimise warehouse operations.
This video highlights the Automation and Innovation initiatives at ST Healthcare in bringing value to customers by improving end-to-end supply chain processes.

This video highlights the Logistics Digitalization initiatives such as digitalization awareness training, integrating academic knowledge into warehouse operations, and recommending cutting-edge technologies like RFID smart zones and autonomous mobile robots.
